    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/1e9e6d8241c9eb44b16331702c4b906f.poster.avif?t=1772266336\" width=1170 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/1e9e6d8241c9eb44b16331702c4b906f.webm?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/1e9e6d8241c9eb44b16331702c4b906f.mp4?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">《Race Max Pro》是一款将 Street、Drift 和 Drag 融为一体的高速、时尚、技巧导向街机竞速游戏。以紧凑操控征服短暂而激烈的比赛，通过深度调校突破极限，并驾驶真实授权车辆称霸赛道。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/ff258b7909b3ba8fcb8fc29ea9e4173c.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=100 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>三种竞速方式</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>掌握三种独特的赛车风格。</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Street 测试你的操控与比赛意识，</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drift 奖励精准与流畅度，</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag 需要完美时机与精准起步。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在模式间即时切换——每一种都会强化不同技巧，让每场比赛都更快速、更刺激。 <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/ad7486bf55c7c3d1a1546480a21e5db6.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=193 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/75565cd77137b21e7cd2050b8630e1f0.poster.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/75565cd77137b21e7cd2050b8630e1f0.webm?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/75565cd77137b21e7cd2050b8630e1f0.mp4?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>单人职业模式</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>踏上完整的单人进阶之路。</strong>击败强劲对手，获取更好的奖励，并在每一章节中解锁更快的赛车。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>限时活动</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>参与轮换的限时活动，完成独特目标并赢取专属奖励。</strong>试驾、每周活动、计时赛、腾空时间、测速陷阱——每一种都锤炼不同技巧，让游戏保持新鲜感。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>赛季</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>完成赛季任务以解锁限量车辆、外观与性能升级。</strong>新奖励将持续推出，让你的车库不断扩张。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/e62d9baa56bfe09e0c59be2ae045e730.poster.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/e62d9baa56bfe09e0c59be2ae045e730.webm?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/e62d9baa56bfe09e0c59be2ae045e730.mp4?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/aaf584b95e7463d23f30ac10afce29dc.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/3477df25684e3d034e046b66fff2e6fd.poster.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/3477df25684e3d034e046b66fff2e6fd.webm?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/3477df25684e3d034e046b66fff2e6fd.mp4?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>真实调校系统</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>按你的方式打造性能。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级引擎、涡轮、变速箱、氮气、轮胎等部件，并根据 Street、Drift 或 Drag 精细调校。每一次升级都会改变车辆在赛道上的真实手感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/dd57df35fa533fb04196824f8627bc08.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=156 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/24ce5eede373adc6688af75752a469f8.poster.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/24ce5eede373adc6688af75752a469f8.webm?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/24ce5eede373adc6688af75752a469f8.mp4?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>视觉自定义</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>以完全自由打造你的风格。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更换车漆、贴膜、轮毂、尾翼等，塑造属于你的竞速身份。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/5cca33046807825fbe3eb9e4ba0f5a3d.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=253 /></span><strong>传奇车辆</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>驾驶来自 BMW、Ford、Nissan、Pagani、Jaguar、Audi、Lotus、Aston Martin、Mazda、Volkswagen 等品牌的官方授权车型。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每辆车都在操控、音效与性能方面被精心还原，让每台机器在赛道上都拥有独特手感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/7a63506ac48541333a637cfe326909ca.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=167 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>多人联赛模式</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在为高速与技巧打造的在线联赛中竞争。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升段位、赢取奖励，并在排名上升时面对更强对手。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>好友对战模式 </strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与好友或对手进行一对一对决。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >设置快速、重复简单——纯粹的街机竞速较量。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/ee11e581f7ba77a3af44f86c163ecd35.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=202 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/ba0afb902bd2ea44ae268322bb14a58c.poster.avif?t=1772266336\" width=780 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/ba0afb902bd2ea44ae268322bb14a58c.webm?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3042650/extras/ba0afb902bd2ea44ae268322bb14a58c.mp4?t=1772266336\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过比赛赚取 Cash、Gold 和 Blueprints——解锁新车、扩充车库，并在每次升级中突破极限。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>打造 · 调校 · 竞速 · 循环。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Street、Drift、Drag 三种竞速类型</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >50+ 款真实授权车辆</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多人模式与排位联赛</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完整自定义与调校系统</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >限时活动与赛季内容</p></li></ul>",
